trans-unit.source: Represents an attribute that is applied to the class definition and determines the <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType*>s of the properties that are of type <xref href="System.Windows.Style"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 클래스 정의에 적용 되 고 결정 하는 특성을 나타냅니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType*>형식의 속성의 <xref href="System.Windows.Style"> </xref>.</xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType*>

trans-unit.source: Control authors apply this attribute to the class definition to specify the <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A>s of the properties that are of type <xref:System.Windows.Style>.
trans-unit.target: 컨트롤 작성자를 지정 <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A>하는 형식이 <xref:System.Windows.Style>.</xref:System.Windows.Style> 속성의</xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A> 클래스 정의에이 특성을 적용

trans-unit.source: For example, if you look at the declaration of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox> class, this attribute is used to specify that the <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerStyle%2A> property is <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBoxItem>.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어의 선언에서는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>클래스,이 특성이 지정 하는를 사용 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerStyle%2A>속성은 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBoxItem>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBoxItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerStyle%2A> 의</xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>

trans-unit.source: Subclasses inherit this definition but can redefine the <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A> of the property by using this attribute on its own class definition.
trans-unit.target: 서브 클래스에서이 정의 상속 하지만 재정의할 수는 <xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A>자체 클래스 정의에서이 특성을 사용 하 여 속성의.</xref:System.Windows.Style.TargetType%2A>
